Package: reportr
Type: Package
Title: RMarkdown templates for statistical report
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Kevin Kunzmann
Maintainer: Kevin Kunzmann <kevin.kunzmann@mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk>
Description: Templates for generating statistical reports or presentations via 
    LaTeX (and beamer). Optimized for wide output to maximize space for graphics.
    Nicely works with git as well.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
